full_text: UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Immigration and Naturalization Service 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA 90012 FILE NUMBER Calendar A A21 557 566 & 567 DATE Feb. 2, 1979 Parimal Manibhai Patel 312 E. Cedar Avenue Apt. T Burbank, Calif. 91502 Please come to the office shown below at the time and place indicated in connection with an official matter. OFFICE LOCATION 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA 90012 Room No. 8024 Floor No. 8th DATE AND HOUR MONDAY, FEBRUARY 26, 1979 - 9:30 A.M. ASK FOR Immigration Examiner REASON FOR Interview regarding your form I-130 visa petitions filed in b@half of: APPOINTMENT Manibhai Shivabhai PATEL and Champa Manibhai PATEL BRING WITH YOU This letter, your citizenship paper and a certified copy of your birth. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU KEEP THIS APPOINTMENT AND BRING THIS LETTER WITH YOU. If you are unable to do so, state your reason, sign below and return this letter to this office at once. I am unable to keep the appointment because: Very truly yours, Jack E. Fortner Assistant District Director for Travel Control SIGNATURE DATE Form G-56 (Rev. 5-1-73) N THIS COPY TO BE MAILED TO THE ATTORNEY OR REPRESENTATIVE, IF ANY
